---
title: Speedy Pepper and Harissa Rigatoni with spicy pangrattato
description: Pangrattato—also known as crispy breadcrumbs—are filled with flavour and crunch. They have many uses across many different cuisines, but in this recipe, they're imbued with harissa spice and used to top this moreish pasta dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R21_W05_IE_IEVQV19447-2_Main__2high-6e9cfd9b.jpg
